<%- include('partials/header') %>

<section class="services-hero" aria-label="Services Introduction">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Our Structural Capabilities</h1>
    <p>Providing precision engineering and modern, custom general contracting services tailored to Florida's unique
      coastal environment.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="service-detail-section section-spacing" id="custom-homes">
  <div class="container detail-grid">
    <div class="text-content">
      <span class="price-indicator">New Construction Blueprinting</span>
      <h2>Architectural Custom Homes</h2>
      <p>We build exceptional contemporary homes that balance clean, minimalist design with the structural strength
        needed for Florida climates. Our build pipelines feature open floor plans, optimized natural light entry points,
        and high-efficiency climate barriers.</p>
      <p>From initial zoning configurations in Wesley Chapel to coastal foundation pouring in Clearwater, our team
        coordinates the entire process from permitting to final inspection.</p>
      <ul class="spec-list">
        <li>Monolithic Foundation Systems</li>
        <li>Impact Window Engineering</li>
        <li>HVHZ Wind-Load Protection</li>
        <li>High-Volume Spatial Planning</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <img class="visual-content"
      alt="Architectural overview of a modern custom-built smart home foundation and framing setup"
      src="/images/construction.webp" />
  </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="service-detail-section section-spacing" id="enhancements">
  <div class="container detail-grid">
    <div class="text-content">
      <span class="price-indicator">Structural Additions & Extensions</span>
      <h2>Premium Spatial Enhancements</h2>
      <p>Maximize your property value and square footage with architectural additions that blend seamlessly into your
        existing home. We specialize in complex engineering challenges, including multi-story expansions and removing
        load-bearing walls to create open concepts.</p>
      <p>Our structural team recalculates load distributions accurately to deliver safe, beautiful open spaces in
        classic properties across Brandon and Tampa.</p>
      <ul class="spec-list">
        <li>Load-Bearing Wall Removals</li>
        <li>Multi-Story Home Additions</li>
        <li>Custom Lanai & Outdoor Living</li>
        <li>Structural Beam Reinforcements</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <img class="visual-content" src="/images/open-concept.webp"
      alt="Interior view of a residential kitchen renovation" />
  </div>
</section>

<section class="service-detail-section section-spacing" id="remodeling">
  <div class="container detail-grid">
    <div class="text-content">
      <span class="price-indicator">Interior Transformation Specs</span>
      <h2>Luxury Architectural Remodeling</h2>
      <p>Transform your interior layout into a sleek, contemporary retreat. We execute high-end kitchen, master
        bathroom, and full-home renovations that focus on premium materials, custom cabinetry, and high-end finishes.
      </p>
      <p>We have extensive experience breathing modern life into historic properties, such as character-rich homes in
        St. Petersburg, while preserving their original structural integrity.</p>
      <ul class="spec-list">
        <li>Minimalist Kitchen Layouts</li>
        <li>Spa-Style Master Bathrooms</li>
        <li>Custom Premium Finishes</li>
        <li>Full-Home Utility Upgrades</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <img class="visual-content" src="/images/bathroom-2.webp"
      aria-label="Finished contemporary bathroom transformation highlighting flat-panel cabinets and natural quartz islands" />
  </div>
</section>

